# Node
after.lock
node_modules
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-lock.yaml
# bun.lock is intentionally NOT ignored: the Dockerfile copies it so
# `bun install --frozen-lockfile` installs pinned, reproducible versions
# (an unpinned install pulls newer deps that break the Turbopack build).

